{"tid":2067448,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"美國運通獲准中國運營銀行卡清算業務","createTime":"2020-06-17T04:19:08.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-17T04:48:13.000Z","uid":1086,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"d8b996403578f1a6b6abdeba1ff550dfafe22666","tid":2067448,"uid":1086,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-17T04:19:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.hkej.com/hkej/images/2020/06/15/2494345_90aa4de67cc7f79d5ff93c0bdc95ec5b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.hkej.com%2Fhkej%2Fimages%2F2020%2F06%2F15%2F2494345_90aa4de67cc7f79d5ff93c0bdc95ec5b.jpg&h=bb4488d0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n中美兩國關係緊張局勢下，中國人民銀行批准美國運通(American Express)在中國設立銀行卡清算業務，為<span style=\"color: red;\">首間獲得銀行卡清算業務許可證的外企</span>。<br />\n<br />\n人行公布，美國運通在中國成立的合資企業<span style=\"color: red;\">連通公司</span>，已經通過人行及銀保監會的審查，將可在中國進行銀行卡清算業務，包括拓展成員機構、授權發行及受理「美國運通」品牌的銀行卡。按照規定，連通公司需要在<span style=\"color: red;\">6個月內正式開始銀行卡清算業務</span>。這反映中國金融業進一步對外開放，深化金融供給側改革，有助提高中國支付服務水平及人民幣國際化。<br />\n<br />\n內地傳媒則報道，騰訊(00700)已經與連通公司達成合作協議，微信支付將可綁定即將推出的美國運通人民幣信用卡。<br />\n<br />\n除美國運通外，萬事達卡(Mastercard)的合資公司萬事網聯在今年2月亦已經獲批籌備銀行卡清算機構，須在1年內完成，然後再向人行申請開業。<br />\n<br />\nPS<br />\n第一階段協議4.4寫左AE/VISA/MASTER 只要申請都要處理,無論成功與否<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d68fd3fd794ae0558305fb59e8c77de272d90eb4","tid":2067448,"uid":44318,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-17T04:19:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"02b6701800704328fd9bff5d2507bb03bc560517","tid":2067448,"uid":282490,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-17T04:20:07.000Z","msg":"有無財經逹人解釋下發生咩事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.g